'From Squeak2.9alpha of 13 June 2000 [latest update: #2992] on 10 November 2000 at 8:38:06 am'!"Change Set:		ScriptorLayoutFix-arDate:			10 November 2000Author:			Andreas RaabA quick fix for tile scriptors centering problem."!!SyntaxMorph class methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified' stamp: 'ar 11/10/2000 08:35'!column: aColor on: aParseNode	| c color |	color _ self translateColor: aColor.	(c _ self newColumn)		parseNode: aParseNode;		layoutInset: self standardInset;		hResizing: #shrinkWrap;		vResizing: #shrinkWrap;		color: color;		borderWidth: 1;		borderColor: c stdBorderColor;		wrapCentering: #topLeft;		cellPositioning: #topLeft.	^c! !